.TH "nvme_init_get_log_power_measurement" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_power_measurement" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_power_measurement \- Initialize passthru command for Power Measurement
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_power_measurement
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_power_meas_log *log "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the log page
.IP "len" 12
The allocated length of the log page
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_POWER_MEASUREMENT
